---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Shared Illumination
---
<p>Notes and essays authored in Markdown (Obsidian-friendly), then published by git.</p>

<h2>Posts</h2>
<ul class="posts">
  {% for post in collections.publishedPosts %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      <div class="meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</div>
    </li>
  {% else %}
    <li class="meta">No posts published yet.</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
